reviewText: BUYER BEWARE!!THIS DVD IS NOT THE ORIGINAL 1938 FILM. IT IS A CARTOON RELEASED IN 2005.

Thinking that I was ordering the 1938 film classic, boy was I shocked and disappointed when I found a rip-off cartoon DVD with the same title in my mail. Amazon, shame on you for not giving out this info to the prospective buyer. Please make it known to customers that what you are selling is not the movie we are being led to believe is available. Film collectors Lawrence and Julia McNally, Yuma,Az.
